title: Nate Bargatze joins the DDFP!
itunes:title: Nate Bargatze joins the DDFP!
description:
In this episode of the DDFP, Dave Dameshek first kibitzes with Eddie Spaghetti about the new Antonio Brown vs Juju Smith-Schuster feud that's been the hot story around the league (3:30). Then, comedian Nate Bargatze, who just released his Netflix special called The Tennessee Kid, sat down with Dave to cover a wide range of topics including his wardrobe choice for the special, his love for Vanderbilt, the Titans and Predators and why he doesn't use curse words (7:45).
